@EndNode

@Node "Next Reply" "Spot.guide/Next Reply"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Next Reply
----------

Keyboard short-cut: Alt Arrow Right

   Go to the next message in the reply thread the current message is
part of.  Spot will link messages on subject or on ^aMSGID kludge.


@EndNode

@Node "Previous Reply" "Spot.guide/Previous Reply"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Previous Reply
--------------

Keyboard short-cut: Alt Arrow Left

   Go to the previous message in the reply thread the current message
is part of.


@EndNode

@Node "Next Marked" "Spot.guide/Next Marked"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Next Marked
-----------

Keyboard short-cut: Ctrl Arrow Right

   Go to the next marked message.  Messages can be marked in the
message list (see @{"Message List Window" Link "Message List Window"}).


@EndNode

@Node "Previous Marked" "Spot.guide/Previous Marked"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Previous Marked
---------------

Keyboard short-cut: Ctrl Arrow Left

   Go to the previous marked message.  Messages can be marked in the
message list (see @{"Message List Window" Link "Message List Window"}).


@EndNode

@Node "Next Unread" "Spot.guide/Next Unread"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Next Unread
-----------

Keyboard short-cut: TAB

   Go to the next unread message in the current area.


@EndNode

@Node "Previous Unread" "Spot.guide/Previous Unread"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Previous Unread
---------------

Keyboard short-cut: Shift TAB

   Go to the previous unread message in the current area.


@EndNode

@Node "Next Unreplied" "Spot.guide/Next Unreplied"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Next Unreplied
--------------

Keyboard short-cut: Alt TAB

   Go to the next unreplied message in the current area.  An unreplied
message is a message directed to you and which you did not reply to
(yet).


@EndNode

@Node "Previous Unreplied" "Spot.guide/Previous Unreplied"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Previous Unreplied
------------------

Keyboard short-cut: Shift Alt TAB

   Go to the previous unreplied message in the current area.  An
unreplied message is a message directed to you and which you did not
reply to (yet).


@EndNode

@Node "Last Message" "Spot.guide/Last Message"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Last Message
------------

Keyboard short-cut: Shift Arrow Right

   Go to the last message in the current area.


@EndNode

@Node "First Message" "Spot.guide/First Message"
@Toc "Move Menu"

First Message
