Keyboard short-cut: Shift Arrow Left

   Go to the first message in the current area.


@EndNode

@Node "Goto Message..." "Spot.guide/Goto Message..."
@Toc "Move Menu"

Goto Message...
---------------

Keyboard short-cut: Right-Amiga G

   Go to a specific message.  You will be prompted for the message
number you would like to jump to.


@EndNode

@Node "Next Area" "Spot.guide/Next Area"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Next Area
---------

Keyboard short-cut: Right-Amiga N

   Go to the next area in the area list.


@EndNode

@Node "Previous Area" "Spot.guide/Previous Area"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Previous Area
-------------

Keyboard short-cut: Right-Amiga B

   Go to the previous area in the area list.


@EndNode

@Node "Area With Unread Mail" "Spot.guide/Area With Unread Mail"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Area With Unread Mail
---------------------

Keyboard short-cut: Right-Amiga U

   Go to the next area in the area list with unread mail left.


@EndNode

@Node "Area With Imported Mail" "Spot.guide/Area With Imported Mail"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Area With Imported Mail
-----------------------

Keyboard short-cut: Right-Amiga I

   Go to the next area in the area list with unread mail from the last
import left.


@EndNode

@Node "Area With Mail For You" "Spot.guide/Area With Mail For You"
@Toc "Move Menu"

Area With Mail For You
----------------------

Keyboard short-cut: Right-Amiga Y

   Go to the next area in the area list with unread mail for you left.


@EndNode

@Node "Area With Unreplied Mail" "Spot.guide/Area With Unreplied Mail"
